GPS Road Builder — authors
==========================

Alexander Kobyakov (Кобяков Александр Викторович)
  <kobyakov@lesburo.ru>, Lesburo — author and maintainer; concept, generalization,
  development and completion of the RidgeSlide method and the QGIS plugin.

Algorithm lineage (see core/ridgeslide/NOTICE):
  - Paul Mach — original Slide approach (paulmach/slide, MIT, 2013).
  - Guo et al. (2020) — density-based corrections adopted by RidgeSlide.
